{"id": 3018, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常中的哪些时候你会有「提前症」？", "description": "什么情况下，你会有「无法忍受一件事始终拖着不做」的「反拖延」心态？（题图来自：iStock ©️ Scar1984）", "record_count": 5549, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191005230301VciJKwhLpmbZxUtM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-06T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5946, "title": "日常中的哪些时候你会有「提前症」？", "content": "日常中的哪些时候你会有「提前症」？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347779, "content": "能自己独立完成、不需要社交的事情，就会想提前办", "image": "img/option/option/20191005212947hWtikgyFK2SD5Aal.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347780, "content": "特别遥远的事情，就总想早做准备（到眼前反而懒得动", "image": "img/option/option/20191005213515MyB6Ch59VY2eqSbD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347782, "content": "开心的事情一定会提前享受完，比如吃零食", "image": "img/option/option/20191005213732sphFOSkziEfjHCAa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347783, "content": "特别闲的时候有事就马上办，这样就能早点躺回去", "image": "img/option/option/2019100521402801uXjy8LZmhavIwi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347784, "content": "一次搞定的事会尽量提前完工（要重复操作的就会拖", "image": "img/option/option/20191005220905Mhf8YNzDdCSsZuwJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347785, "content": "坐飞机/赶火车这类定时任务，一定会提前两个钟到", "image": "img/option/option/20191005221320cFQ6YNdHyZJWa8ul.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347788, "content": "如果接下来有娱乐，为了痛快玩耍就会把 deadline 提前", "image": "img/option/option/20191005222829Q2ZmKxLp8kEz4gi1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347789, "content": "不光自己有提前症，还没法忍受跟拖延的人一起干活儿", "image": "img/option/option/20191005223212to9LqhTRErYFfGpP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347790, "content": "完全没有，我做啥都不会提前", "image": "img/option/option/201910052233554fiVpKwqQ61JeXBS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}